SUMMARY:Salsa at Brooklyn Basin
DESCRIPTION:Salsa at Brooklyn Basin. Please visit The Original Brooklyn Basin Boardwalk Salsa Dancing for further details and updates (if the weather is bad\, sudden cancellations\, etc). We try and keep up with the latest updates\, but it’s best to check the site for the most up to the minute information. \nGenerally hours are 12-4pm/1pm-5pm for the colder months/winter and 2-6pm during the warmer months/summer. Generally\, Spring time event hours are 3-7pm. \n  \n 
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-at-brooklyn-basin/2026-04-05/
LOCATION:Brooklyn Basin\, 288 9th Ave\, Oakland\, CA\, United States
CATEGORIES:San Francisco
