SUMMARY:Viva Esencia Sunday Social
DESCRIPTION:VIVA ESENCIA LONDON welcome you to the current edition of our very popular Salsa Social \nOFFICIAL WEBSITE :\nhttps://www.esencialibre.co.uk/salsa-party-london/\nEveryone knows the DJ is what makes the party – because the tunes are everything. In October we have DJ Sam Sleek. \nThe venue – especially for dancers in mind – it’s got a beautiful sprung floor and lovely high ceilings for ventilation. Located in Somerstown Community Sports Centre just 6 minutes walk from Euston train station and 8 mins walk from Kings Cross\, this venue is perfectly centrally located for easy access. \nGoing straight in for the social\, we’ll start the music from 14:00 with no classes or shows and go all the way through to the end. We want you to walk away dance happy and filled with joy! \nWe have no bar facilities on site\, so please do bring your own refreshments.\nTickets are available online and on the door.\nPre-register online: £10\nOn the door: £12 CASH/Tap&Pay\n—-\nTime: 14:00 – 18:00\nAddress: Somers Town Community Sports Centre\, 134 Chalton St\, London NW1 1RX\nClosest Tube: Euston station (5 min walk)\nOther: NO BAR at venue\, please bring your own drinks (Water Dispenser available)
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/viva-esencia-sunday-social/2026-04-05/
LOCATION:Somers Town Community Sports Centre\, 134 Chalton Street\, London\, NW1 1RX\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:London
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/617179181_1509560764505943_7738495085468821803_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
