SUMMARY:"Art & Salsa" Dance Class & Social
DESCRIPTION:A fun experience of bachata and salsa dancing at Buckhead Art & Company\, an award-winning fine art gallery in Buckhead ATL. 1st Sundays of every month. \nNOTE: This is a 21+ event. Outside food & drinks are not allowed (No BYOB). VIP Admission includes complimentary cocktails. \nDon’t miss this electrifying evening of bachata and salsa dancing with Fuego y Hielo Dance Company! Whether you’re a beginner or expert\, this dance experience will cater to all skill levels. You will learn basic steps and techniques\, ensuring a fun and engaging experience for everyone. \nFuego y Hielo Dance Company was founded in 2014 by directors Fuquan Ferrell and Candace Joyner. It has quickly become Atlanta’s premier Afro-Latin Dance group. They have performed and taught all over world spreading their unique style of dancing. \nAfter the class will be a social mixer to showcase your new dance skills and enjoy the vibrant ambiance of Buckhead Art + Company. Great opportunity to connect with fellow dance enthusiasts and art lovers! \nVIP Admission includes: \nEntry to Class and Dance Social\nComplimentary Wine Bar by Sip + Share Wines (@SipAndShareWines)\nComplimentary drinks from Insolito Tequila (@Insolito)
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/art/2026-04-05/
LOCATION:Buckhead Art & Company\, 288 Buckhead Avenue Northeast\, Atlanta\, GA 30305\, Atlanta\, GA\, 30305\, US
CATEGORIES:Atlanta
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/454407656_1040077774790938_214994741367505727_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
